name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 88: Apple Sauce Bandits

content.html:
Dear Internet,On this weeks episode, we talk about getting revenge on apple sauce bandits, going to the shop, and whether someone looks like a cowboy.We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet.Sincerely,The coHosts- Nick, Jennifer, Michael, and Tim Lanning!Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!
